---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact - Skief Labs" description="Book a 30-minute discovery call. If the friction is real, it's worth a conversation.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/sk9.jpg" alt="Discovery call" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-900/40"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-36 text-center w-full">
      <h1 class="page-hero-title heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-linen mb-8 leading-[1.1] uppercase">
        If the friction is real, it's worth a conversation.
      </h1>
      <p class="page-hero-body text-linen/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Most teams reach out when something that used to work has stopped working at scale — and the manual workarounds are no longer sustainable. If that's where you are, this is the right next step.
      </p>
      <div class="page-hero-cta flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="#book" class="cta-book-btn btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Book a 30-minute discovery call
          <span class="cta-arrow text-lg inline-block transition-transform duration-300">→</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-linen/60 text-sm italic">No pitch. No obligation. Just clarity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT THIS CONVERSATION IS -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] border-l-4 border-neon pl-4">
            What this conversation is
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 text-navy-900/80 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-navy-900 text-xl font-serif italic">It's a diagnostic, not a demo.</p>
          <p>We won't walk you through our capabilities or show you what we've built for other people. We'll ask questions about your specific situation — how your business operates, where effort is concentrated, what's breaking — and tell you honestly whether we think we can help.</p>
          <p>Sometimes the answer is no. We're comfortable with that.</p>
          <p>Either way, you leave with a clearer picture of what's worth fixing — and what isn't.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO THIS CALL IS FOR -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Left card: Good fit -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-navy-900/15 p-8 md:p-10 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-navy-900 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#001233]">
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900 mb-8 tracking-[0.15em] text-center">This conversation makes sense if you are</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-5 text-navy-900/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-neon mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>A founder, operator, or senior leader at a B2B company</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-neon mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Dealing with a real, recurring data or outbound problem</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-neon mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Looking for clarity, not a vendor pitch</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-neon mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Ready to invest in fixing the system, not just patching it</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Right card: Not a fit -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-navy-900/15 p-8 md:p-10 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-navy-900 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#001233]">
          <h3 class="subhead-condensed text-sm text-navy-900/60 mb-8 tracking-[0.15em] text-center">It's probably not worth your time  if you are</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-5 text-navy-900/70 text-base leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-4 h-0.5 bg-red-500 mt-3 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Running an RFP or comparing vendors on price</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-4 h-0.5 bg-red-500 mt-3 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Looking for free consulting or a speculative proposal</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-4 h-0.5 bg-red-500 mt-3 shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Hoping for quick fixes over durable solutions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT HAPPENS AFTER -->
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Heading block -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="inline-block">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
              <p class="subhead-condensed text-xs text-navy-900 tracking-[0.2em]">Next Steps</p>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-3 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-center">
              What happens after the call
            </h2>
            <div class="flex justify-end">
              <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-navy-900"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p>If there's a fit, we'll outline a clear next step — either a scoped Data Intelligence build or a Sales Acceleration pilot, depending on where the problem lies.</p>
          <p>If there isn't a fit, we'll say so directly — and often point you toward something more useful.</p>
          <p class="text-navy-900 font-semibold">There's no obligation either way.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-left">We'd rather have a short, honest conversation that goes nowhere than a long one that leads somewhere it shouldn't.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy-900 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CALENDLY / CTA -->
  <section id="book" class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[2.2rem] text-navy-900 mb-8 leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em]">
        Book your discovery call
      </h2>
      <p class="text-navy-900/70 text-base md:text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Choose a time that works for you. The call takes 30 minutes.
      </p>

      <!-- Calendly inline embed -->
      <div class="calendly-inline-widget max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10" data-url="https://calendly.com/skief/discovery-call?hide_gdpr_banner=1&background_color=faf8f5&text_color=001233&primary_color=3366FF" style="min-width:320px;height:700px;"></div>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>

      <p class="text-navy-900/60 text-base">
        Or reach us directly: <a href="mailto:contact@skieflabs.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-200">contact@skieflabs.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
